{"tid":604099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滲入新義安做卧底 探員被「紅棍」懷疑係鬼","createTime":"2018-03-24T11:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T06:55:47.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"450e9b54d0095e6946b984269e61c7e342ad53ef","tid":604099,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/192320_806b0fb3a90a3eb17a219e94806ddcb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F192320_806b0fb3a90a3eb17a219e94806ddcb3.png&h=24944919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方於2014年派出卧底潛伏葵青及荃灣黑幫，成功拘控一批男子。繼本周一有8人認罪後，昨再有6人承認另外17項自稱三合會成員等罪名。案情透露卧底探員於行動期間曾多次遭案中被告懷疑其真正身份，更有「紅棍」對他直言：「我覺得你係鬼嚟。」卧底屢次化險為夷，最終在眾人被捕後指認出各人。<br />\n<br />\n昨日認罪6名被告為關鈃勻（21歲）、李錦秋（59歲）、黃根財（39歲）、管世傑（47歲）、廖立人（40歲）及蔡思良（50歲），分別報稱電腦維修員、退休人士、裝修工及運輸工等，案件押後至6月7日求情。另一名報稱商人的39歲被告陳國熙則不認罪，案件今日開審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">促到拳館學舞獅貢獻社團</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/192450_31eb2296300fb4dc6037be01b9cf59d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F192450_31eb2296300fb4dc6037be01b9cf59d9.png&h=50acafbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方於2014年8月派出化名「阿Joe」的卧底探員滲入葵青及荃灣黑幫，首先認識已於本周初認罪的男子陳繼豪。11月1日，卧底獲陳邀請到一間餐廳與李會面，李向卧底說：「我大環山老新嘅，財哥（即被告黃根財）係我老表。你哋掛朵跟財哥，我就係你哋二叔。」李又謂：「我係棍嚟，遲啲齊人一次過出老尖做儀式。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/192433_600ce204efd79c5fc104ab1f5bc5569b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F192433_600ce204efd79c5fc104ab1f5bc5569b.png&h=e2f15049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數日後李向卧底介紹黃：「呢個就係財哥，你大佬。」黃則對卧底說：「如果你做得好，有機會好似我咁，紮職㗎。我係426棍嚟，畀心機喇，我睇好你。」三合會專家指等於自稱為新義安紅棍。同月29日，李向卧底介紹拳館師傅「寶哥」陳國熙，陳要求卧底加入拳館學舞獅，以對社團有所貢獻。但當晚李及陳一度質疑卧底的真正身份，李查問卧底後說：「我冇話你係鬼，只要你哋忠心為公司就得喇。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/192522_7367a216d7124a5cc71de84bf8314cf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F192522_7367a216d7124a5cc71de84bf8314cf5.png&h=e56c830f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180322/20339349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F20339349&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=ce2af4ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F20339349&h=eed110f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180322/20339349</a>"},{"pid":"222dffc00975918e565fb97349e52888a9889d17","tid":604099,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:26:24.000Z","msg":"翌月9日，在一個新義安成員生日會上，黃對卧底說：「阿Joe，老實講，我覺得你係鬼嚟。」卧底答：「我唔係。」黃說：「咁你要證明你自己唔係鬼喇，我𠵱家畀個柯打你，你同我收班死士返嚟，我要你做行動組，有冇問題？」卧底答：「我盡做啦。」最終行動於2015年7月公開，卧底於認人手續中認出各被告。"},{"pid":"670c8e19e58d4ffabf62f7c5b7d30a722be35e1e","tid":604099,"uid":2155,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"幅圖真島嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bd339b88ec45549970d9a1ce01d7b6b9773c5d","tid":604099,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"真吾？"},{"pid":"dbbbddbd6ac67d15fdd4cc1f7c88280a98b367bc","tid":604099,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"做乜撚個卧底畫到成個真島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f95485e803a33ad919efe875a4e0